This repository describes the workflow and analyses of the 1000 genomes of Neisseria gonorrhoeae

The aim of this project was investigate global transmission dynamics of Neisseria gorrhoeae in the period 2015 - 2018.

Data preparation

Data preparation: Collection info, alignment, recombination masking, snp-calling are described in the paper (link to come).

Phylogeny

The phylogenetic tree was produced by using FastTree v.2.1 Scaling of the genetic distance to time was done using LSD2 with two clades constrained to date estimates derived in previous studies (see paper text).
